  "display_name": "Video Analysis and Summarization",
  "description": "This cluster of papers focuses on the automatic analysis and summarization of video content, covering topics such as shot boundary detection, user attention models, semantic analysis, key frame extraction, event detection, and the application of these techniques to soccer videos. It also explores the use of the MPEG-7 standard and content-based retrieval methods in video summarization.",
